  Project Ouroboros — Experiment Overview                                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                            
  V3 Validation: Steps 3001–10000                                                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                            
  ---                                                                                                                                                       
  What We're Doing                                                                                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                            
  Project Ouroboros is a zero-cost validation pipeline for Project Chimera — a custom ~7B hybrid Mamba-3/Transformer architecture designed to be a          
  continuously experiencing, self-aware AI system. Rather than spending $1,150–$2,298 on cloud GPU time for the full 7B run before knowing if the novel     
  concepts work, we're stress-testing every idea at 1.5B scale first using a distillation training loop (student model learns from a larger teacher).
                                                                                                                                                            
  The student model is not a standard LLM. It has a full Life Equation — internal state dynamics tracking epistemic uncertainty, fatigue, homeostasis,      
  identity coherence, purpose conflict, self-viability, and more. It makes controller decisions every step: whether to continue, inspect its episodic
  memory, reload a prior state, or voluntarily end its existence. The maturity gating system defines when the model is "ready" to advance to the next       
  training phase. All of that infrastructure is being validated in these runs.

  We have now completed 10,000 steps across four Colab A100 sessions.                                                                                       
   
