  Interpretation: The student made consistent progress through step 6000 (best val KL ever: 0.3625). After that it plateaued and slightly regressed, ending 
  at 0.3979. This is expected behavior at this training stage — the learning rate is decaying aggressively (from 4.06×10⁻⁵ at step 6000 down to 2.58×10⁻⁵ at
