  What Went Right
                                                                                                                                                            
  - Stability: 10,000 steps, zero NaN, clean gradients. failure_containment passes at every single checkpoint. The Mamba-3 hybrid blocks, attention anchors,
   and the full Life Equation forward pass are all computing correctly.                                                                                     
  - Identity coherence: coh = 1.000, D_id = 0.0000 — the identity anchor is rock solid. Identity drift metric passes at every eval.
  - Distillation signal: val KL improved consistently from 0.38 to 0.36, confirming the student is learning from the teacher.                               
  - VOLUNTARY_END dramatically reduced: 22.7% → 5.1% across the experiment, even before the logit bias fix.                                                 
  - Checkpoint infrastructure: Automatic saves every 1,000 steps, best-loss tracking, forensic bundle logging every 40 "fire" events — everything works.    
  - Variant switchover: Transitioning mid-run from phase4_infrastructure to round3_full at step 5001 was clean. No state corruption, no loss spike.         
                                                                                                                                                            
